<includeonly>{{#show:Category:{{{category|}}}|?Display label|default={{{category|}}}}}</includeonly><noinclude>
Returns a category's display label, falling back to the raw category
name if no `Display label` annotation is set.

This is a Tier A primitive — returns a plain string for use in headings,
breadcrumbs, or any custom display markup.

Parameter:
* category - The category name (without `Category:` prefix)

Example:
 <h1>{{Category/label|category=Book}}</h1>
</noinclude>
